# Next.js v0 Starter Template

## Stack
- Next.js 15+
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Vercel deployment
- Yarn package manager

## Code Style
- Strict TypeScript
- Functional over OOP
- English comments only
- Clean functions (no side effects)

## Project Structure
/src
  /app - Next.js App Router
  /components - Reusable UI
  /lib - Core utilities
  /api - API routes 